{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 64,
  "title": "第六十四章（守微）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "其安易持，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其未兆易謀，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其脆易破，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其微易散。"
    },
    {
      "text": "為之於未有，"
    },
    {
      "text": "治之於未亂。"
    },
    {
      "text": "合抱之木生於毫末；"
    },
    {
      "text": "九層之臺起於累土；"
    },
    {
      "text": "千里之行始於足下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "為者敗之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "執者失之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人無為故無敗，"
    },
    {
      "text": "無執故無失。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之從事，常於幾成而敗之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "慎終如始，則無敗事。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人欲不欲，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不貴難得之貨；"
    },
    {
      "text": "學不學，"
    },
    {
      "text": "復眾人之所過；"
    },
    {
      "text": "以輔萬物之自然。"
    },
    {
      "text": "而不敢為。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治身治國安靜者，易守持也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "情欲禍患未有形兆時，易謀止也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禍亂未動於朝，情欲未見於色，如脆弱易破除。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其未彰著，微小易散去也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲有所為，當於未有萌芽之時塞其端也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治身治國於未亂之時，當豫閉其門也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從小成大。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從卑立高。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從近至遠。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有為於事，廢於自然；有為於義，廢於仁；有為於色，廢於精神也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "執利遇患，執道全身，堅持不得，推讓反還。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不為華文，不為色利，不為殘賊，故無壞敗。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人有德以教愚，有財以與貧，無所執藏，故無所失於人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從，為也。民之為事，常於功德幾成，而貪位好名，奢泰盈滿而自敗之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "終當如始，不當懈怠。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人欲人所不欲。人欲彰顯，聖人欲伏光；人欲文飾，聖人欲質樸；人欲色，聖人欲於德。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不眩為服，不賤石而貴玉。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人學人所不能學。人學智詐，聖人學自然；人學治世，聖人學治身；守道真也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 18,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "眾人學問反，過本為末，過實為華。復之者，使反本也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 19,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "教人反本實者，欲以輔助萬物自然之性也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-21",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人動作因循，不敢有所造為，恐遠本也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
